## 🚀 项目简介 | Introduction

`finer` 旨在构建一个高度自动化的投研数据中台，将社交媒体创作者（KOL）零散、口语化且非标的投资观点（如 B站视频、微信长图、雪球贴、**飞书群文件**等），转化为具备**高度结构化、可回测、可审计**的“投资事件”（Investment Events），并自动同步至 **NotebookLM** 构建个人知识库。

`finer` is designed to build a highly automated investment research data platform that transforms scattered, colloquial, and non-standard investment opinions from social media creators (KOLs)—including Bilibili videos, WeChat images, Xueqiu posts, and **Feishu chat files**—into **highly structured, backtestable, and auditable** "Investment Events," with automatic synchronization to **NotebookLM** for personalized knowledge base building.

<p align="center">
  <img src="docs/assets/feishu_sync.png" width="600" alt="feishu-sync-pipeline">
</p>

---

## 🏗️ 核心架构 | Architecture

系统由 6 个解耦的核心模块组成：
The system consists of 6 decoupled core modules:

```mermaid
flowchart LR
  A["模块 1: 数据注入 | Ingestion"] --> B["模块 2: 多模态解析 | Parsing"]
  B --> C["模块 3: 数据清洗 | Cleaning"]
  C --> D["模块 4: 模型抽取 | Extraction"]
  D --> E["模块 5: 人机评审 | Review (RLHF)"]
  E --> F["模块 6: 自动回测 | Backtesting"]
```

---

## 🛠️ 技术栈 | Tech Stack

- **核心语言 | Core**: Python 3.11+ (Polars / Pydantic V2)
- **大模型引擎 | AI**: DashScope (Qwen-VL-Max) / OpenAI
- **结构约束 | Constraint**: `Instructor`
- **数据处理 | Data**: `Data-Juicer`
- **标注评审 | Review**: `Argilla` (SFT & RLHF)

---

## ⚡ 快速上手 | Quick Start

```bash
# 克隆项目 | Clone
git clone https://github.com/kelipovanatalja453-bot/finer.git
cd finer

# 安装 | Install
pip install -e .

# 配置飞书与 NLM (可选) | Config Feishu & NLM (Optional)
cp configs/feishu.yaml.example configs/feishu.yaml
# 编辑 configs/feishu.yaml | Edit configs/feishu.yaml

# 运行同步 | Run Sync
finer feishu-sync
```

